headline: Zoetis to Participate in the Piper Sandler 36th Annual Healthcare Conference
summary: PARSIPPANY, N.J., November 19, 2024--Zoetis Inc. (NYSE:ZTS) will participate in the Piper Sandler 36th Annual Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, December 3, 2024. Wetteny Joseph, Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, will represent the company and respond to questions from analysts at 11:30 a.m. ET.
